### Critical Fixes
- **handleSlHit race condition**: Market close FIRST, then cancel orders (was creating ghost positions)
- **Grading R-multiples**: Now computed from stored prices per signal (was hardcoded to old 1.5/2.5/4.0)
- **Gate B rr_tp1**: Threshold 1.5→0.8 to match tightened TP1 at 1.0R (was blocking ALL signals)
- **Reconciler auto-close**: Orphan positions auto-closed after 30min, ORPHAN_SKIP_SYMBOLS env var
- **ESM dotenv hoisting fix**: ORPHAN_SKIP reads env at call time, not import time
- **Callback auth**: Trailing newline in Vercel env var caused all callbacks to 401
- **btc_4h_change backfill**: 173/173 signals now have BTC 4h data (was 93% NULL)

### TP Ladder Change
- **1.0/2.0/3.5R** (from 1.5/2.5/4.0R) — capture profits before reversal
- Gate B, grading, researcher all updated to match

